                  </hi>. I am a lighterman in the employ of Thomas Pope—I was sent to Pickle Herring-wharf to drive the boys out of the barg—when I had left the barge there were a quantity of coals in her—when I got back some of them were gone—the policeman brought a bag into the counting-house—I saw him take a boy from the barge.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
