                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable T</hi> 43.) On the 5th of February I went to the barge and saw several boys in the act of filling a bag with coals; Berry was one—the lightermen drove them away—I collared Berry and took him to the wharf—Eddy got over to the stairs—I went round and secured him—I saw them both put coals into the bag—I</p>
